  <glossary>
  <definition id="fs-idm60057472">
  <term>money multiplier formula</term><meaning id="fs-idm4982256"> total money in the economy divided by the original quantity of money, or change in the total money in the economy divided by a change in the original quantity of money</meaning>
  </definition>
